Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper is about object detection on mobile devices using a novel search space and architecture. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper involves automated architecture search and the use of a latency-aware search algorithm. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves the development of efficient object detection models for mobile devices. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper involves the use of a search algorithm to optimize the architecture of the object detection model. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper involves the development of a mobile-friendly object detection model for multimedia applications.
